msgctxt "sn35.126:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 35 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 35 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.126:0.2"
msgid "13. Gahapativagga "
msgstr "13. Householders "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 126. Nāḷandasutta → nālandāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "sn35.126:0.3"
msgid "126. Nāḷandasutta "
msgstr "126. At Nālandā "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn35.126:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā nāḷandāyaṃ viharati pāvārikambavane. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Nālandā in Pāvārika’s mango grove. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.126:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho, upāli gahapati, yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinno kho, upāli gahapati, bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then the householder Upāli went up to the Buddha … and asked him, "

msgctxt "sn35.126:1.3"
msgid "“ko nu kho, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme no parinibbāyanti? "
msgstr "“What is the cause, sir, what is the reason why some sentient beings aren’t fully extinguished in the present life? "

msgctxt "sn35.126:1.4"
msgid "Ko pana, bhante, hetu, ko paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme parinibbāyantī”ti? "
msgstr "What is the cause, sir, what is the reason why some sentient beings are fully extinguished in the present life?” … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn35.126:1.5"
msgid "(Yathā purimasuttantaṃ, evaṃ vitthāretabbaṃ.) "
msgstr "(This should be told in full as in SN 35.124.) "

msgctxt "sn35.126:1.6"
msgid "“Ayaṃ kho, gahapati, hetu ayaṃ paccayo yena m’idhekacce sattā diṭṭheva dhamme parinibbāyantī”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn35.126:1.7"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
